<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Rosemont</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Located to the Northwest of Chicago, Rosemont is one of the friendliest and inclusive neighborhoods in the region, perfect for families looking for a quaint, peaceful location to call home. Rosemont is bordered by Cambrian Drive, 23rd Avenue, Northmount Drive and 14th Street. Rosemont’s location on an elevated spot allows inhabitants to have stunning views of mountains and hills, making it not just a family-friendly community, but also one that is very beautiful and scenic as well.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">The average price of homes in Rosemont, one of Calgary’s most sought-after neighborhoods, is $780,000 as per the latest reports. There are plenty of options for buyers – single family homes, condos and semi-detached homes among them. Some of the houses in Rosemont retain their old appearance, simply waiting for buyers who can transform them with their creativity and fresh ideas. As a place that has excellent connectivity, and retains its clean, calm environment despite its proximity to downtown Calgary, Rosemont is a place with high potential for real-estate investment.</p>
        </div>
